{"tid":1592770,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣建議]解決國際上，香港反送中運動趨向的弱勢","createTime":"2019-09-24T18:26:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T02:18:36.000Z","uid":89882,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"ec9f139d2d4b574511d258aef6d702ca5c615512","tid":1592770,"uid":89882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T18:26:23.000Z","msg":"認真<br />\n<br />\n要達到5大訴求<br />\n<br />\n真係要煲大<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙普選</span></span></strong><br />\n用大量文宣令市民相信，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">普選</span></strong>先係解決呢次問題嘅最終手段<br />\n<br />\n原因: 無雙普選=將來呢個<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無民意授權</span></strong>嘅政權<br />\n終有一日又會再推惡法<br />\n<br />\n到時唔通又要再抗爭<br />\n而如果他朝真係有另一條惡法<br />\n<br />\n我相信今次輸左 乜都爭取唔到嘅話<br />\n香港只會一條又一條嘅惡法被通過<br />\n<br />\n所以<br />\n唔該大家<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">文宣、傳單、twitter國際戰線</span></span></strong>嘅方向<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>除左繼續煲大 警隊暴力 獨立調查委員會</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但唔該和位手足</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">將落實<span style=\"color: orange;\">雙普選</span>為現在運動嘅焦點 清楚單一目的<br />\n<br />\n只有雙普選 先係可以由<span style=\"color: violet;\">根本體制內</span>解決現存嘅問題</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n而係國際舞臺上面 爭取<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">普選</span></strong>呢種爭取自由民主，會<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">擴大</span></strong>近13個月來以手足嘅血同性命換返<br />\n黎嘅核彈，令外國近來減少留意香港近況嘅人<br />\n<br />\n明白需要國際關注係普選對香港人嘅重要性同逼切性，而焦點會更為<strong>昇華</strong>至自由民主<br />\n<br />\n#爭取雙普選<br />\n#認同請幫推<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FeUzPKZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFeUzPKZ.jpg&h=6679b225&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0cc29f21b6d05984eece61afd54431734f51759b","tid":1592770,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"cited